Configure Your Digital Experience Sites After Vlocity Insurance Application Suite Group Voluntary Benefits Installation

There are a few configuration steps for the Digital Experience Sites that you create for your users.

Enable Standard External Profiles for Group Voluntary Benefits:
Before you can start letting users access your new Experience Site, you need to enable the Digital Experience setting.

Update the Experience Site for Vlocity Insurance Application Suite Group Voluntary Benefits:
After you receive your spin, you need to complete the following steps twice: once for the Digital Broker Self-Service Portal and once for the Digital Policyholder Self-Service Portal.
title: Configure Insurance Digital Experience Sites
